{"tid":1325514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用緊Facebook的人都犯有叛國罪 香港原來有大批外國勢力支持者","createTime":"2019-07-17T01:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T01:54:45.000Z","uid":250752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c39ae778bcb3438f7dcf835939a5250464f43c47","tid":1325514,"uid":250752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【明報專訊】美國總統特朗普昨在Twitter讚facebook創始董事蒂爾（Peter Thiel）消息靈通，華府將「查究」Google有否叛國。公開支持特朗普的富豪蒂爾周日指控Google為拓中國大陸業務，「決定跟中國軍隊而非美國政策合作」、「似乎叛國」。<br />\n<br />\n他質疑中國等情報機構已滲透Google人工智能項目，解放軍或從而竊走美國非出口的技術，促聯邦調查局、中央情報局調查。Google股價昨跌1%；公司發聲明否認。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilentmajorityhk%2F&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=8fed4d43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkgpaocom%2F&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=d12ed807\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/</a><br />\nReport 曬佢唔該"}]}